WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:11.573
The presence of the Lord filled my house so strong; I can honestly tell you I've never felt the presence of the Lord like that ever before, and it shook me.

00:00:11.573 --> 00:00:20.560
It gave me a renewed fear in Him of how close we are to Jesus' coming.

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:29.320
I saw in my prayer time, when the glory manifested in my house so strong, He warned me about coming up higher again.

00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:33.319
This is the second time He said it since Thursday.

00:00:33.319 --> 00:00:42.350
Today is Wednesday, and we're going in, so it's been six days since He spoke to me the last time, since I had my visitation from the Lord.

00:00:42.621 --> 00:00:44.805
He said, 'It's time to come up higher.

00:00:44.805 --> 00:00:52.260
' He said it again: 'It's time to come up higher in the prophetic realm, in walking with Me.

00:00:52.260 --> 00:00:58.731
For it is in the coming up higher and abiding in the fire that I long for you to be.

00:00:58.731 --> 00:01:06.234
' Then, all of a sudden, I saw the heavens split right above me when I was praying.

00:01:06.234 --> 00:01:14.284
I'm talking about a massive break in the atmosphere, and I saw the Spirit of the Lord.

00:01:14.573 --> 00:01:19.285
I saw the Lord seated on His throne—Great God Jehovah, not Jesus.

00:01:19.285 --> 00:01:24.773
I saw this massive light coming out and I saw Him seated on His throne.

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:32.719
Now I want you all to really grasp what I'm telling you because I'm going to tell you something that is going to shock you.

00:01:33.079 --> 00:01:39.840
You need to understand how much God loves us and how much He cares for us.

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:46.027
He said Heaven is going to invade Earth now, not in the future.

00:01:46.027 --> 00:01:55.209
He said it's invading Earth now; it's time for an invasion of Heaven on Earth like we've never seen before.

00:01:55.644 --> 00:02:06.325
I saw lava coming out of the throne of God with what looked like a staircase in front of Him.

00:02:06.325 --> 00:02:08.799
It was tiered.

00:02:08.799 --> 00:02:17.111
When I was looking up in the throne room, there was a liquid lava flowing out of the throne that looked like liquid honey.

00:02:17.111 --> 00:02:46.280
It was like honey, but it was moving like molasses—slow but beautiful—and it had sparkles of gold dust and beautiful things all inside of this honey-like substance coming out of the throne.

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:55.819
It was oozing out on the Earth.

00:03:06.468 --> 00:03:13.293
Then the Lord allowed me to see inside of Him.

00:03:13.293 --> 00:03:25.578
Now, a lot of you are going to probably squawk about this, but I really don't care; you need to know how much Jesus loves you.

00:03:29.928 --> 00:03:35.919
God is light, and in Him, there is no darkness at all.

00:03:47.885 --> 00:03:48.410
He allowed me to see the light.

00:03:56.823 --> 00:03:58.040
The light of God is like His skin.

00:03:58.040 --> 00:04:30.430
Our skin is flesh like this, but then He allowed my spiritual eyes in this vision to see inside of the Father, the great Elyon, the Most High God.

00:04:30.430 --> 00:04:46.484
I say this with the most fear and reverence of anything I've ever spoken.

00:05:00.180 --> 00:05:03.445
I want you to hear this: God is light, and it's like His skin.

00:05:03.445 --> 00:05:07.784
That's what I'm trying to bring down to a human level for you.

00:05:07.784 --> 00:05:20.240
I'm telling you something that I saw in the spirit realm at a human level.

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:43.085
In this, I saw the level of light was like this, and when you went inside of Him, He was endless.

00:05:43.085 --> 00:05:53.862
There is no beginning and there is no end.

00:05:53.862 --> 00:05:58.899
He is like His own dimension.

00:05:58.899 --> 00:06:10.255
The Father is His own dimension in Himself; He is endless.

00:06:10.255 --> 00:06:30.236
Inside of Him, it looked like a different kind of light, a light that I've never seen before.

00:06:30.236 --> 00:06:57.320
In this light, there were different lights inside of the light, and they looked like stars, but each star was different and it was shining all inside of Him.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:20.840
A different, brighter light was shining all inside of the light, and it moved like it was alive.

00:07:23.599 --> 00:07:26.428
The light was transparent; it was spirit.

00:07:30.354 --> 00:07:45.150
It moved, it had a shape, and it was taking form, but it was transparent in the way the light was moving.

00:07:45.150 --> 00:07:49.044
This is so hard to explain.

00:07:56.960 --> 00:08:25.368
It was moving, and then I could see the light inside of Him; there was no end to it, like if you were to see inside a room that had no ending and no beginning.

00:08:35.973 --> 00:08:36.853
He allows me to see the silhouette of His face from afar.

00:08:36.853 --> 00:08:56.984
In the spirit, I can see His silhouette and His chin, but on His head was like a crown.

00:08:59.864 --> 00:09:19.383
In His head, where I could see, were three beautiful blue sapphires—the most beautiful blue sapphires I've ever seen.

00:09:19.383 --> 00:09:36.570
They were huge; one was a little smaller, one was bigger, and one was a little smaller.

00:09:44.386 --> 00:09:47.150
All around it was this beautiful light, but it was like fire—blue fire.

00:09:47.930 --> 00:09:53.439
It was making those sapphires on His head glow.

00:09:54.400 --> 00:10:04.745
All around His face, on the chin, I could not see eyes or His forehead.

00:10:12.809 --> 00:10:19.205
I could see the back of His head, but everything else was fire.

00:10:19.205 --> 00:10:24.296
Around the chin, it was radiating a blue fire.

00:10:25.431 --> 00:10:37.167
It looked like light piercing out, so bright and captivating it would burn your eyes.

00:10:46.364 --> 00:11:02.079
Then He allowed me to see this: there was a blue fire coming off of His head, like sapphire fire, all coming off the chin from here down.

00:11:02.079 --> 00:11:24.520
I was fixed on it because when the Lord allows you to see something like this, I was trying to remember everything I could; it was captivating.

00:11:24.520 --> 00:11:42.455
I could feel the presence of the Lord so strong I felt like I was melting like wax in my home.

00:11:42.455 --> 00:11:58.104
It was literally pouring out on me so strong it was everything I could do to stand underneath it.

00:11:58.104 --> 00:12:19.745
A lot of people will say, 'Oh, there's no possible way what you saw was the Lord,' but I didn't see His face.

00:12:19.745 --> 00:12:43.560
What I'm trying to tell you is that the Lord, for whatever reason in the most holy moment in my life, allowed me to see a glimpse of Him.

00:12:43.560 --> 00:12:58.880
He's so much more, but I saw a glimpse of something that was so holy and beautiful.

00:13:07.076 --> 00:13:07.440
For a moment, I saw the silhouette of the Father.

00:13:07.440 --> 00:13:19.462
I tried my best to describe what I saw in the spirit.

00:13:19.462 --> 00:13:44.880
When I was praying, I was interceding for Israel, and all of a sudden He said, 'I want you to focus and see this wall.

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:57.062
' Upon this wall, He said, 'This is eons and eons of time.

00:13:57.062 --> 00:14:02.399
' This is Angelic writing.

00:14:02.399 --> 00:14:16.810
It was written on this stone wall, but it was in a language I've never seen before.

00:14:16.810 --> 00:14:38.365
It was triangles engraved into the wall with fire, similar to how He etched the language on the Ten Commandments.

00:14:38.365 --> 00:14:56.149
This was writing on a granite rock—triangles, circles in the triangles, and waves like water waves.

00:14:56.149 --> 00:15:17.439
It was all in a different language, and He told me it was an ancient text that has been there for millions of years.

00:15:17.439 --> 00:15:35.636
I still don't have the revelation of why He showed this to me, but He wanted me to see this writing on the wall.

00:15:40.620 --> 00:15:48.880
It was all in little lines, one after another, in some kind of Angelic language.

00:15:49.375 --> 00:16:02.055
It was fascinating because I got to stare at it for a bit in the spirit realm.

00:16:02.055 --> 00:16:17.888
All this was being downloaded like a massive fire hydrant just soaking you down because you're underneath the glory.

00:16:34.027 --> 00:16:34.493
I'm seeing all this coming out of His throne.

00:16:34.493 --> 00:16:39.739
He said, 'Heaven is invading Earth.

00:16:39.739 --> 00:16:55.302
' One of the things He said to me was, 'My prophetic people are thinking too carnal.

00:16:55.302 --> 00:17:02.580
They are too carnal right now.

00:17:02.580 --> 00:17:12.759
It's time to come up another level.

00:17:12.759 --> 00:17:26.098
' He was even speaking to me: 'You're thinking too carnal, too shallow.

00:17:26.098 --> 00:17:53.166
' He said, 'Do you know the difference between somebody who is just a flash in the pan versus somebody who is going to stand the test of time in ministry?

00:17:53.166 --> 00:18:04.920
' He said, 'Do not be a flash in the pan.

00:18:04.920 --> 00:18:18.104
Be somebody that is going to be a pillar and teach the Word.

00:18:18.104 --> 00:18:47.493
' He brought up Brother Kenneth Hagin and said Brother Hagin didn't always get a word every single day for the body of Christ to tell on a TV or radio program; he taught the Word.

00:18:47.493 --> 00:19:02.826
He taught the people how to live by faith, how to stand on the covenant, and how to plead the blood.

00:19:08.320 --> 00:19:11.908
To stand the test of time in ministry, you must teach the people the Word.

00:19:11.908 --> 00:19:20.630
It's not all about being a flash in the pan.

00:19:20.630 --> 00:19:31.800
There are too many flash-in-the-pan prophetic people who burn out.

00:19:31.800 --> 00:19:48.170
You must get in the Word and teach the people how to pray.

00:19:48.170 --> 00:20:16.363
He said, 'When you seek Me daily and you're at My feet, getting out of the carnal thinking of your mind and coming up higher in the prophetic, I will give you those words.

00:20:16.363 --> 00:20:35.070
' He said it is a must in this season because we are in a season that has never been on this Earth before.

00:20:35.070 --> 00:20:48.803
We're entering a time of great birthing pains, more than what we've ever seen.

00:20:48.803 --> 00:20:57.712
What we've experienced so far is nothing compared to what's about to happen.

00:21:05.550 --> 00:21:34.440
He did not say this in fear, of course, because perfect love casts out all fear, but He said it as a warning for people to come up higher, to be saturated in that presence at His feet.

00:21:34.440 --> 00:21:48.688
People don't know what that means: separating yourself unto Him, making Him first in your life.

00:21:48.688 --> 00:21:50.770
Make Him priority.

00:21:50.770 --> 00:21:53.633
He's number one.

00:21:53.633 --> 00:22:03.360
How hungry and desperate are you for the things of God?

00:22:04.760 --> 00:22:06.880
It has to be every breath.

00:22:06.880 --> 00:22:29.200
There is a level of prophetic that is ankle-deep, knee-deep, waist-deep, and then over the head, going straight to the bottom in those deeper waters.

00:22:29.200 --> 00:22:45.621
He said, 'Brandon, there's so much more than what you're seeing on YouTube.

00:22:45.621 --> 00:22:54.386
There's so much more than what you've had.

00:22:54.386 --> 00:23:06.239
' The words I've given you all are just scratching the surface.

00:23:06.239 --> 00:23:11.480
If you abide in Me and My words abide in you...

00:23:11.480 --> 00:23:31.790
abiding in the secret place of the Most High, being seated with Him in heavenly places far above all principalities and powers.

00:23:31.790 --> 00:23:55.943
Take that seat of dominion and authority in these last days, walking with Him and letting Him abide in you.

00:23:55.943 --> 00:24:00.488
It's like a breath—inhale, exhale.

00:24:00.488 --> 00:24:09.293
He said, 'This is where you're going to go.

00:24:09.293 --> 00:24:20.600
You'll get the words from Me if you abide in the real prophetic.

00:24:20.600 --> 00:24:28.794
You get the words from Me and give them out to the people.

00:24:28.794 --> 00:24:40.135
You don't come on the carnal level looking for a word.

00:24:40.135 --> 00:24:53.213
You sit at My throne, and that's when you give it to the people.

00:24:53.213 --> 00:25:03.880
' It was all happening while I was underneath the glory.

00:25:03.880 --> 00:25:25.960
Going back to the three sapphires, I believe it was a representation of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Ghost; all three are one.

00:25:25.960 --> 00:25:29.458
They were in Him.

00:25:32.480 --> 00:25:35.248
It was a crown over His head.

00:25:37.039 --> 00:25:42.380
It was the most beautiful thing I've ever seen.

00:25:44.000 --> 00:25:59.863
My words in the English vocabulary do not do it justice; it falls so short.

00:25:59.863 --> 00:26:04.240
Hi, my name is Brandon.

00:26:18.173 --> 00:26:18.511
I saw some things when I was praying, and I was translated in my spirit eyes.

00:26:33.731 --> 00:26:34.166
I was in this jungle-like place and I was being ushered in, pushed very quickly.

00:26:34.166 --> 00:26:46.305
All of a sudden, I see this temple in front of me.

00:26:53.960 --> 00:27:02.551
I go into this temple that was like beautiful platinum—not gold or silver, but almost transparent.

00:27:02.551 --> 00:27:07.577
I've never seen that on this Earth before.

00:27:17.790 --> 00:27:18.060
I went into this temple and saw a being on a throne.

00:27:19.140 --> 00:27:22.547
He was high and lifted up.

00:27:24.949 --> 00:27:29.600
I looked and glimpsed, and I thought in my spirit, 'Where am I?

00:27:29.600 --> 00:27:32.103
Who is this?

00:27:32.103 --> 00:27:42.195
' And He said, 'I AM THAT I AM.

00:27:42.195 --> 00:27:50.263
' When He said that, it shook the whole temple.

00:27:52.068 --> 00:27:58.024
The foundation was being shaken by His words.

00:27:58.024 --> 00:28:02.926
I screamed because it was so powerful.

00:28:02.926 --> 00:28:18.412
I glanced up to the top and could see gold and a beautiful red ruby.

00:28:18.412 --> 00:28:33.129
Then there was a light beyond any light I've ever seen before.

00:28:33.129 --> 00:28:43.560
There's nothing on this Earth as bright as what I saw.

00:28:43.560 --> 00:28:59.140
You can look at the sun at noon and it's still not as bright.

00:29:15.303 --> 00:29:35.039
There were three stages of light: an outer light, a brighter light, and then a center light that was so bright it was piercing.

00:29:35.039 --> 00:29:44.080
If you looked at it, it would melt you.

00:29:44.080 --> 00:29:53.066
I couldn't look directly at it; it was incredible.

00:29:53.066 --> 00:30:04.775
When He spoke, His words would go out and stay alive.

00:30:04.775 --> 00:30:35.640
At the base of the altar, there was water that was ankle-deep, knee-deep, waist-deep, and then it went way down deep.

00:30:35.640 --> 00:30:48.373
In this water, you could take your whole body to the bottom.

00:30:48.946 --> 00:31:11.457
The water was the clearest, bluest water I've ever seen; it was living water flowing out of the throne.

00:31:11.457 --> 00:31:31.919
When He spoke to me for about an hour, He told me a lot of things about the end times, the church, and personal things.

00:31:31.919 --> 00:31:51.044
His words would come out of that light in English, but they would be big, then get smaller and turn into seeds upon the water.

00:31:51.044 --> 00:32:03.707
The words wouldn't die; they remained alive and started to grow.

00:32:03.707 --> 00:32:14.079
They would grow roots like a potato or a peanut.

00:32:14.079 --> 00:32:36.104
Every time He would speak, they would just start to form and they would go on each other; they would all start to grow together.

00:32:36.104 --> 00:32:45.206
Out of that light, a massive eyeball came out.

00:32:55.600 --> 00:32:56.754
It was an all-seeing eye that came right within 15 feet of me.

00:33:00.744 --> 00:33:13.647
It was so intense I wanted to cry out in repentance and ask for mercy.

00:33:13.647 --> 00:33:25.199
In the iris of the eyeball, there was fire moving and dancing.

00:33:32.650 --> 00:33:39.590
He talked to me about a verse because I had been hearing from certain ministers that there is no end-time revival.

00:33:40.370 --> 00:33:45.731
I was asking Him about this.

00:33:55.768 --> 00:33:58.529
I quoted scriptures, but He was speaking to me in tongues.

00:33:58.529 --> 00:34:11.934
His language was deep and masculine, like roaring thunder or living water.

00:34:11.934 --> 00:34:22.754
Even though it was a heavenly sound, I understood everything He was saying.

00:34:22.754 --> 00:34:42.294
We were talking to each other; I understood Him in English in my ears, but it was in tongues.

00:34:42.294 --> 00:34:54.719
He said, 'Son, you have no idea the real translation of that scripture.

00:34:54.719 --> 00:35:20.880
You need to go back to the Greek and study My Word more than just the King James or the Amplified.

00:35:29.267 --> 00:35:34.724
You need to study the meaning of each word.

00:35:34.724 --> 00:35:48.450
' He said, 'Who says I'm coming back right now?

00:35:48.450 --> 00:36:24.656
' I mentioned the signs of the times, and He said, 'I am in control of time.

00:36:24.656 --> 00:36:45.044
' He shook the foundation of the temple: 'I am in control of time.

00:36:45.044 --> 00:36:56.217
' He said, 'I will come back when I am ready.

00:37:05.160 --> 00:37:15.440
I said in My Word that I'm coming back for a spotless bride, and the bride is not ready yet.

00:37:15.440 --> 00:37:26.800
' He said He would show me something.

00:37:26.800 --> 00:37:45.926
There was a preacher interceding on the Earth, and the Lord allowed me to hear the prayer.

00:37:45.926 --> 00:38:08.480
A shaft of light like a flaming comet came up from the Earth and circled the throne room.

00:38:08.480 --> 00:38:21.947
These prayers were echoing in the throne room.

00:38:21.947 --> 00:38:42.291
In the spirit, this man came to the throne room and a globe wrapped around him.

00:38:42.291 --> 00:39:07.555
Beams of light were coming out of his belly and shooting to places on the globe: South America, Europe, Asia, America, and Canada.

00:39:09.445 --> 00:39:14.640
He was interceding for an end-time revival.

00:39:14.640 --> 00:39:41.509
The Lord told me to tell a certain family member that their theology that there's no revival is nonsense.

00:39:41.509 --> 00:39:58.011
There will be a great harvest of souls and an outpouring of My Spirit.

00:39:58.011 --> 00:40:03.159
We will walk in great victory.

00:40:03.159 --> 00:40:14.800
He said, 'A lot of people have an escape mentality.

00:40:14.800 --> 00:40:22.628
You will not have an escape mentality.

00:40:22.628 --> 00:40:30.733
You will press into Me and walk in My glory.

00:40:30.733 --> 00:40:46.513
I never designed the armor for retreat; I designed it for charging ahead and taking dominion.

00:40:46.513 --> 00:41:06.416
' When He said the teaching that there is no revival is nonsense, it shook the foundation with His anger.

00:41:06.416 --> 00:41:16.080
He said there's a great shifting and shaking coming.

00:41:16.599 --> 00:41:20.974
I saw a corn being shucked.

00:41:20.974 --> 00:41:26.059
He said, 'I'm going to shuck the corn, son.

00:41:26.059 --> 00:41:36.915
' He's going to pull it back and clean it up for preparation.

00:41:36.915 --> 00:41:42.145
Then He showed me the bride.

00:41:42.145 --> 00:41:52.582
She had a beautiful lace gown, but there were black smudges on it, like soot.

00:41:52.582 --> 00:42:03.440
He said, 'I told you in My Word I'm coming back for a spotless bride.

00:42:03.440 --> 00:42:13.060
It's time to come out of the ankle-deep water and come to the deeper water.

00:42:13.060 --> 00:42:26.968
' I told Him I wanted to go in that deep water, and He said, 'Brandon, you've been there before.

00:42:26.968 --> 00:42:30.000
It's like muscle memory.

00:42:30.000 --> 00:42:36.113
' He then spoke to me about finances.

00:42:43.880 --> 00:42:45.988
I had been asking for a million-dollar idea, and He was stern.

00:42:45.988 --> 00:42:55.269
He said, 'Where in My Word did I tell you to pray like that?

00:42:55.269 --> 00:43:03.079
Seek first the Kingdom, and all these things will be added.

00:43:03.079 --> 00:43:11.350
Seeking finances as idolatry is the way you're doing it.

00:43:11.350 --> 00:43:21.186
Seek Me, and I will give you the secret things.

00:43:24.099 --> 00:43:28.462
I have no problem blessing you, as long as the money doesn't have you.

00:43:28.462 --> 00:43:36.140
' I apologized and said I wanted to be used.

00:43:40.280 --> 00:43:44.640
Jesus is coming back for a victorious church, not a retreating one.

00:43:54.040 --> 00:43:54.280
The gospel that must be preached is repentance.

00:43:54.280 --> 00:44:06.773
If you lay your head upon His chest, He will speak secret things in a whisper.

00:44:06.773 --> 00:44:28.039
I was interceding for America, and He told me, 'I will not let America become a goat nation, for your founding fathers made a covenant with Me.

00:44:28.039 --> 00:44:41.451
' He took me to Plymouth Rock and I saw the pilgrims making a covenant and taking communion.

00:44:41.451 --> 00:44:44.791
Those prayers still echo.

00:44:48.970 --> 00:44:54.062
I saw George Washington crying out on the battlefield, and God gave him victory.

00:44:54.062 --> 00:45:06.399
The Lord said those men died for freedom, and He will not let their blood go.

00:45:13.031 --> 00:45:13.288
He said, 'You think pain is judgment?

00:45:13.288 --> 00:45:18.040
True judgment is separation from Me for eternity.

00:45:18.040 --> 00:45:21.930
This is just correction.

00:45:21.930 --> 00:45:29.040
' He said there is a great shaking coming.

00:45:29.040 --> 00:45:38.192
Great revival beyond anything you can comprehend is coming.

00:45:38.192 --> 00:45:44.697
No man will get the glory for it.

00:45:44.697 --> 00:45:49.435
I saw glory domes where people were healed by the power of God.

00:45:49.435 --> 00:45:55.691
This was happening throughout the whole world.

00:45:55.691 --> 00:46:02.079
Please subscribe to our channel if this video blessed you.

00:46:02.079 --> 00:46:14.848
Jesus Christ is coming, and I hope you're ready.

00:46:14.848 --> 00:46:26.314
There is no once-saved-always-saved if you have no walk with Him.

00:46:34.129 --> 00:46:34.560
You can backslide.

00:46:34.560 --> 00:46:46.435
I'm telling you the truth because I see Him and talk to Him.

00:46:46.435 --> 00:46:49.808
I'm not here to condemn you but to lift you up.

00:46:49.808 --> 00:46:54.520
Don't compromise and live in sin.

00:46:54.520 --> 00:47:03.896
People who practice sin daily without repentance are on the highway to hell.

00:47:04.560 --> 00:47:13.436
We are supposed to keep our lamps full like the virgins.

00:47:14.600 --> 00:47:18.429
The wages of sin is death.

00:47:20.933 --> 00:47:25.733
Jesus said, 'Go and sin no more, lest a worse thing come upon you.

00:47:25.733 --> 00:47:36.520
' We have to live separate and for Him.

00:47:36.520 --> 00:47:40.388
It's not a game anymore.

00:47:40.388 --> 00:47:43.817
Get your heart right.

00:47:52.573 --> 00:47:54.640
Father, we thank You that You are a loving God, full of mercy.

00:47:54.640 --> 00:48:02.503
You healed all our diseases and took our infirmities.

00:48:02.503 --> 00:48:11.653
No weapon formed against us shall prosper.

00:48:25.263 --> 00:48:25.634
We take authority over the devil and demonic spirits coming against our children.

00:48:27.719 --> 00:48:30.870
We call in the wayward children and unsaved loved ones.

00:48:31.140 --> 00:48:40.617
We speak for laborers to cross their path.

00:48:45.497 --> 00:48:53.890
We pray for husbands and wives to have a revelation of the glory of God.

00:48:55.940 --> 00:49:00.480
We plead the blood of Jesus over them.

00:49:10.359 --> 00:49:10.759
We call for restoration of marriages and households.

00:49:14.960 --> 00:49:17.710
We are the salt and light of this Earth.

00:49:18.693 --> 00:49:31.727
We thank You that we are joint heirs with Jesus Christ.

00:49:38.760 --> 00:49:45.506
Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:49:53.390 --> 00:49:53.680
We take authority over addictions and depression.

00:49:53.680 --> 00:50:02.828
I thank You for spiritual babies growing into adults through this channel.

00:50:18.386 --> 00:50:23.440
We realize who we are in Christ and take our authority.

00:50:30.195 --> 00:50:32.065
We are not afraid of the devil.

00:50:32.065 --> 00:50:40.400
We thank You for Your goodness and mercy.

00:50:43.427 --> 00:50:47.640
We renew our minds and come up higher.

00:50:53.020 --> 00:50:53.214
In Jesus' name, Amen.

00:51:07.411 --> 00:51:08.526
I hope this blessed you.

00:51:08.526 --> 00:51:19.805
It's time to go deeper and spend more time in the Word.

00:51:19.805 --> 00:51:29.960
Jesus loves you, and we will see you next time.

00:51:29.960 --> 00:51:33.465
Have a blessed day.
